UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularBassSynth_C.Sync.Descripti: Adjusts the degree of synchronization between oscillators.

UserOptionDefinition.Device_ModularBassSynth_C.Overdrive.Desc: Sets the amount of distortion applied to the signal.
